# Session [30] – Network+

## Main Topics
- VPN chist?  
- Types of VPN: Site-to-Site va Remote Access  
- Tarze kar va estefadeh-ha dar network  

## Flashback – VPN Basics
- VPN = Virtual Private Network  
- Connection encrypted va secure baraye data beyne network ha  
- Routers, firewalls, ya software VPN client anjam midahand  

## Explanation

### Site-to-Site VPN
- Do network ro be ham vasl mikonad → LAN to LAN  
- Routers ya firewalls VPN gateway mishavand  
- All traffic be sorat automatic az VPN tunnel migozarad  
- Estefadeh: connecting branch offices  

### Remote Access VPN
- User ya device farar dar jaye dige → be LAN vasl mishavad  
- VPN client baraye encrypt connection estefade mishavad  
- Estefadeh: employees dar khane ya travel  

### Example Table
| Type        | Connection | Users | Estefadeh |
|------------|------------|-------|-----------|
| Site-to-Site | LAN-LAN  | Few networks | Branch offices |
| Remote Access | User-LAN | Single users | Telecommuting, mobile |

### Estefadeh-ha
- Secure internet access  
- Protect sensitive data  
- Connectivity baraye distributed networks  

